        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>

all the frames are stacked on top of each other.

when the user clicks on the drawing frame we pass the click through to the current back frame.

if there is no current back frame then we iterate through all the back frames checking if the click can find a poly to select</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
